Package pl.lejczak.project

Interface Structure

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BubbleStructure, InsertionStructure
    public interface Structure
    Structure interface, component for SortingFactory. It is used to create sorting algorithm. It stores data and defines the operations performed by the algorithm on the data.
    Author:
    Maciej Lejczak
